description: [``botocore``] U7i instances with up to 32 TiB of DDR5 memory and 896 vCPUs are now available. C7i-flex instances are launched and are lower-priced variants of the Amazon EC2 C7i instances that offer a baseline level of CPU performance with the ability to scale up to the full compute performance 95% of the time.
[``botocore``] This release adds Timestream for LiveAnalytics as a supported target in EventBridge Pipes
[``botocore``] Extend DescribeClusterNode response with private DNS hostname and IP address, and placement information about availability zone and availability zone ID.
[``botocore``] Initial release of AWS Tax Settings API
